title: Did you take a picture of the visitors a ghost and find the car keys in the woods?
subtitle: :: Federal leaflets telling the story of a missing woman, the appearance of a ghost, and an abandoned car in an unknown location.
author: Jordan Liles
vclaim: After the photographer discovered a ghost figure in a photograph, he returned to the site, found the keys to a car that matched an abandoned car, and knew that a woman had mysteriously disappeared nearby.
